The paper deals with the study of acyclicity parameters of hypergraphs, which is a topic in both theoretical computer science and artificial intelligence. The paper also mentions the usefulness of these parameters in database theory. Therefore, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DB (Databases) are likely sub-categories. The paper also involves the study of graph classes and their properties, which falls under cs.CG (Computational Geometry) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
